{"about_the_game":"MechAvenger is a fast paced VR shooter and platformer about fighting robots after the end of humanity. Shoot, punch, jump and climb your way through the enemy horde, and shut down their factory.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716730/extras/combat1.gif?t=1704898938\" /><br><br>Take down enemies with 9 unique weapons, using your quick reload belt to keep them firing! Bash your enemies with weapons and fists to knock them to the ground. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716730/extras/Stun1.gif?t=1704898938\" /><br><br>The robotic horde is plentiful, but ammo is not.  Search your environment for extra weapons and ammo. Kill stunned enemies with a melee hit for an ammo bonus!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716730/extras/combat2.gif?t=1704898938\" /><br><br>Navigate platforming sections by climbing and flinging yourself off walls. Swing with the grappling hook to cross long pits and build speed. Get yourself out of harms way with your servo powered dodge.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716730/extras/climbing5.gif?t=1704898938\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716730/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1704898938","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716730/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1704898938","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716730/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1704898938","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2716730/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1704898938","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Tracked Controller Support","id":52},{"description":"VR Only","id":54}],"c